se.sics.assertionServer.actions
Class AssertionServerAction

java.lang.Object
  se.sics.assertionServer.actions.AssertionServerAction

public class AssertionServerAction
extends java.lang.Object

Class for collecting information about an action (e.g. create/delete attribute, set/delete attribute value, get attribute values) that the assertion server can perform.
